Build an AI-powered Side Effect Pattern Tracking system for a medication management application called Synapse AI.

Requirements:

* Users can log:

  * Medications taken
  * Dosage
  * Time taken
  * Mood (1-10 scale)
  * Energy level (1-10 scale)
  * Sleep quality (1-10 scale)
  * Symptoms and side effects

* Store historical medication and symptom data.

* Create an analytics engine that identifies patterns between:

  * Medication timing
  * Specific medications
  * Reported symptoms
  * Mood
  * Sleep
  * Energy levels

* Generate insights such as:

  * "You report headaches 80% of the time within 3 hours of taking Medication X."
  * "Poor sleep quality is frequently associated with increased nausea."
  * "Energy levels tend to improve on days when Medication Y is taken on schedule."

* Display findings in:

  * Interactive charts
  * Weekly trend reports
  * Monthly health summaries

* Include confidence scores for all AI-generated insights.

* Design a clean, mobile-friendly dashboard using modern UI/UX principles.

* Use scalable architecture that supports future machine learning model integration.
